        Parameters:
        sprite - Image representing the tower.
        initial_tower_range - Initial range of the tower.
        initial_tower_firing_speed - Initial firing speed of the tower.
        initial_tower_damage - Initial damage dealt by the tower.
        tower_cost - Cost of the tower.
